import React, {useState} from 'react'; import axios from 'axios'; import { useNavigate } from 'react-router-dom'; const RegistrationForm = () => { const navigate = useNavigate(); const [formData, setFormData] = useState({ firstName: '', lastName: '', username:'', password:'', email:'', favoriteGenres:[], favoriteActors:[], preferredLanguage:[], preferredNews:[], }); const [userExists, setUserExists] = useState(false); const handleChange = (e) => { const {name, value, options} = e.target; if(e.target.multiple){ const selectedOptions = Array.from(options).filter(option => option.selected).map(option => option.value) setFormData({...formData, [name]: selectedOptions}); } else{ setFormData({...formData, [name]: value}) } } const handleSubmit = async(e) => { e.preventDefault(); const response = await axios.post('http://localhost:3001/register', formData); if(response.data.userFound === true){ setUserExists(true); } else{ navigate('/LoginForm'); } } return (
